{{Quote|''A DeathRun inspired game with randomized room layouts every roundǃ Avoid the Spirit's traps and escape the haunted mansion with your soul intactǃ Submitted for Spookality 2024‚ 2+ Players Required to play․''}}

Spook Em Up is a deathrun style group [[:Category:Game worlds|game world]], created by Crazium for [[Spookality 2024]].

==Overview==
[[File:Spook_Em_Up_gameplay1.webp|thumb|left|Pre-game lobby for Spook Em Up.]]
Spook Em Up involves two groups of players: Lost Souls, and Spirits. The objective of the Lost Souls is to make it through various trapped rooms to escape the haunted mansion. The objective of the Spirits is to prevent the Lost Souls from escaping by triggering traps as they go. Lost Souls cannot see the Spirits, who lurk in the walls, but the Spirits can see the Lost Souls as they traverse each room. Each trap can only be triggered once, so it's prudent for Spirits to be certain about when to trigger the traps.

==Trivia==
* Spook Em Up was the 4th place winner of VRChat's Spookality 2024 Fractured Realm world jam, along with nine other worlds.

